<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1878-06-03T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1878-06-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="151" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d151">
                    <head>No. 146.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Evarts</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Taylor</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1878-06-03"><hi rend="italic">June</hi> 3,
                            1878</date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p rend="flushleft"><hi rend="smallcaps">Taylor</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Minister, Berlin:</hi></p>
                    <p>Express, through proper channel, the earnest congratulations of the President
                        and American people on His Majesty’s providential escape.</p>
                    <closer><signed>EVARTS.</signed></closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>